<%- include('../layout/header'); -%>
  <!-- Page Header Start -->
  <div class="container-fluid page-header mb-5 p-0" style="background-image: url(/client/img/carousel-1.jpg)">
    <div class="container-fluid page-header-inner py-5">
      <div class="container text-center pb-5">
        <h1 class="display-3 text-white mb-3 animated slideInDown">Rooms</h1>
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
          <ol class="breadcrumb justify-content-center text-uppercase">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Pages</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item text-white active" aria-current="page">
              Rooms
            </li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Page Header End -->

  <!-- Room Start -->
  <div class="container-xxl py-5" style="margin-bottom: 200px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
        <h6 class="section-title text-center text-primary text-uppercase">
          Phòng Của Chúng Tôi
        </h6>
        <h1 class="mb-5">
          Khám Phá <span class="text-primary text-uppercase">Các Loại Phòng</span>
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-4">

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
          <div class="room-item shadow rounded overflow-hidden h-100">
            <div class="position-relative">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="/client/img/room-1.jpg" alt="Phòng Single" />
              <small
                class="position-absolute start-0 top-100 translate-middle-y bg-primary text-white rounded py-1 px-3 ms-4">500.000đ/Đêm</small>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 mt-2">
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-3">
                <h5 class="mb-0">Phòng Single</h5>
                <div class="ps-2">
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <small class="border-end me-3 pe-3"><i class="fa fa-bed text-primary me-2"></i>1 Giường Đơn</small>
                <small class="border-end me-3 pe-3"><i class="fa fa-bath text-primary me-2"></i>1 Phòng Tắm</small>
                <small><i class="fa fa-wifi text-primary me-2"></i>Wifi</small>
              </div>
              <p class="text-body mb-3">
                Lý tưởng cho khách du lịch một mình, phòng Single ấm cúng cung cấp không gian nghỉ ngơi thoải mái và
                riêng tư.
              </p>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-end"> <a class="btn btn-sm btn-dark rounded py-2 px-4"
                  href="/booking?type=Single">Đặt Ngay</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
          <div class="room-item shadow rounded overflow-hidden h-100">
            <div class="position-relative">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="/client/img/room-2.jpg" alt="Phòng Double" />
              <small
                class="position-absolute start-0 top-100 translate-middle-y bg-primary text-white rounded py-1 px-3 ms-4">800.000đ/Đêm</small>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 mt-2">
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-3">
                <h5 class="mb-0">Phòng Double</h5>
                <div class="ps-2">
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <small class="border-end me-3 pe-3"><i class="fa fa-bed text-primary me-2"></i>1 Giường Đôi</small>
                <small class="border-end me-3 pe-3"><i class="fa fa-bath text-primary me-2"></i>1 Phòng Tắm</small>
                <small><i class="fa fa-wifi text-primary me-2"></i>Wifi</small>
              </div>
              <p class="text-body mb-3">
                Thiết kế hiện đại , phòng Double mang đến sự thư giãn tuyệt đối với giường cỡ lớn.
              </p>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-dark rounded py-2 px-4" href="/booking?type=Double">Đặt Ngay</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
          <div class="room-item shadow rounded overflow-hidden h-100">
            <div class="position-relative">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="/client/img/room-3.jpg" alt="Phòng Suite" />
              <small
                class="position-absolute start-0 top-100 translate-middle-y bg-primary text-white rounded py-1 px-3 ms-4">1.500.000đ/Đêm</small>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 mt-2">
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-3">
                <h5 class="mb-0">Phòng Suite</h5>
                <div class="ps-2">
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <small class="border-end me-3 pe-3"><i class="fa fa-bed text-primary me-2"></i>1 Giường King</small>
                <small class="border-end me-3 pe-3"><i class="fa fa-bath text-primary me-2"></i>1 Bồn Tắm</small>
                <small><i class="fa fa-wifi text-primary me-2"></i>Wifi</small>
              </div>
              <p class="text-body mb-3">
                Trải nghiệm sự sang trọng với phòng Suite, bao gồm khu vực tiếp khách riêng biệt và bồn tắm thư giãn.
              </p>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-dark rounded py-2 px-4" href="/booking?type=Suite">Đặt Ngay</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.7s">
          <div class="room-item shadow rounded overflow-hidden h-100">
            <div class="position-relative">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="/client/img/image3.jpg" alt="Phòng Deluxe" />
              <small
                class="position-absolute start-0 top-100 translate-middle-y bg-primary text-white rounded py-1 px-3 ms-4">3.000.000đ/Đêm</small>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 mt-2">
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-3">
                <h5 class="mb-0">Phòng Deluxe</h5>
                <div class="ps-2">
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                  <small class="fa fa-star text-primary"></small>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                <small class="border-end me-3 pe-3"><i class="fa fa-bed text-primary me-2"></i>2 Giường Đôi</small>
                <small class="border-end me-3 pe-3"><i class="fa fa-bath text-primary me-2"></i>2 Phòng Tắm</small>
                <small><i class="fa fa-wifi text-primary me-2"></i>Wifi</small>
              </div>
              <p class="text-body mb-3">
                Rộng rãi và cao cấp, phòng Deluxe hoàn hảo cho gia đình hoặc nhóm bạn, mang đến tầm nhìn toàn cảnh, hiện
                đại, văn minh
              </p>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-dark rounded py-2 px-4" href="/booking?type=Deluxe">Đặt Ngay</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
